<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-scissortest.xml">ScissorTest</db:link> type enables scissor test, which discards fragments outside the rectangular area of the screen specified by the left, bottom, width and height properties.</db:para>
</db:section>
